Used admin to merge.  The only failure was a new link added in this PR which failed to verify.

@RDIL 	We could adjust the test for this scenario so that if the URL has `?AddedInPr=8618` where the PR matches the current PR number, it ignores the failure.  Most sites will ignore the query string for static content.

